McMad is thankful it is a short walk. He had chosen to stay near the cave and was planning on camping there again tonight anyway. He had been scouting, helping the Coldain locate the Frost Giant camps. Finally reaching the cave entrance he carefully lays Selilya on an outspread fur, covering her gently with another. <br>
